name: Laby10s
description:
Created for the Ludum Dare 51 with theme "Every 10 seconds".

Use keyboard arrows or buttons on screen to move left or right.

Go to the star to win each labyrinth.

You have only 10 seconds to add movements to the list before going to an other labyrinth.

Have fun and don't forget to breath a little.

Game available for Windows, Mac and Android.

Developed in Delphi 11.2 Alexandria with love from France.
